(10, 1, '2009-06-24 01:20:27', '2009-06-24 05:20:27', 'Welcome to Texans Air Conditiong and Heating, locally owned since 1991.  We service all of Northwest Houston, from Katy all the way to Champions Forest.  Major credit cards accepted, and financing is available on equipment repair - all brands.\r\n\r\nMake an appointment today by calling 832-473-7554.\r\n\r\nTACL B 11762E', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2009-06-24 01:22:11', '2009-06-24 05:22:11', '', 0, 'http://texanshvac.com/?page_id=10', 1, 'page', '', 0),
